{"tid":2280180,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"關員涉藏對講機被控 友人甘冒再遭起訴風險出庭作供圖證清白","createTime":"2020-11-10T10:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T10:36:53.000Z","uid":56115,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b75747ae2424ff7b4fa9fd0bd7e7d87db53837dd","tid":2280180,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T10:07:35.000Z","msg":"去年中秋節，有人聚集在紅磡海韻軒酒店附近，向結婚擺酒的警員「祝賀」贈慶。有休班海關當日與友人駕駛電單車途經現場，遭警方截查，發現他們各管有一部對講機，同被控無牌管有無線電通訊器具罪。<span class=\"red\">案中關員的友人早前已獲撤控、准以簽保行為了事，昨卻甘冒再被檢控的風險出庭作供，自言當日將裝有對講機的腰包放進被告背囊內，被告對此毫不知情</span>。辯方今結案陳詞指，「管有」必須「知情」，加上對講機存放位置隱密，在警署內才被搜出，間接證明被告或許真的不知情。<br />\n<br />\n被告的中學同學伍展邦早前獲准簽保撤控，昨日上庭為林作供。鄭官警告，<span class=\"red\">伍可能會因證供內容再被檢控。</span>"},{"pid":"89c083591ea28cad10f232cf19fb8a98e55c0e59","tid":2280180,"uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T10:07:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201110/EHF4D54SOVAG3N4GEIVEVIZ4IU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201110%2FEHF4D54SOVAG3N4GEIVEVIZ4IU%2F&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7IgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=642866e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201110%2FEHF4D54SOVAG3N4GEIVEVIZ4IU%2F&h=f6b6fe71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201110/EHF4D54SOVAG3N4GEIVEVIZ4IU/</a>"},{"pid":"c8cc8efac99b2dbf9b6a7cdb8b91fccb55909310","tid":2280180,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"一世人兩兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d949719e56e01cf1df64d8088c4852449235cd54","tid":2280180,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T10:09:22.000Z","msg":"再提一提依單係<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">鄭念慈</span></span>審"},{"pid":"a568137c9d06c15ef4af133610479eb093219ec6","tid":2280180,"uid":